title: Best free agents still available
itunes:title: Best free agents still available
description:
A room filled with heroes - Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Colleen Wolfe discuss the latest news from the NFL, including Arian Foster visiting the Dolphins and Rex Ryan’s comments on Ryan Fitzpatrick. Then, the heroes go over the St. Louis Graybeards roster before NFL Media’s Conor Orr joins the show to update his “Madden” team.
